        "subject": "LU-19385 tests: skip sanity-lnet/226 for old client",
        "message": "LU-19385 tests: skip sanity-lnet/226 for old client\n\nExcept sanity-lnet/226 for clients older than 2.15.62-31.\nThis was excluded for newer clients with older servers,\nbut not for older clients running with newer servers.\n\nAdd this to the sanity-lnet.ex list, and add some debugging to\nthis subtest in case there are more test failures.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nTest-Parameters: clientversion=2.16 testlist=sanity-lnet env=VERBOSE=true\nFixes: 2b210f3905 (\"LU-17440 lnet: prevent errorneous decref for asym route\")\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@thelustrecollective.com>\nChange-Id: Ic5ea7be017cf89ea8437480f761012dc1c7909ef\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
